Custom Methods:

Syntax:
Access-Modifier    Specifier   Return-Type   MethodName(Parameters){

            Code Fragment that can perform the task
    }

    Access-Modifiers: public, protected, private, default
            public : always visible
            protected:
            private: with the same class
            default:


    Specifier: static, final, abstract, synchronized
    static: no need for object to be created, belongs to the class / call through class

    Return-Type: void, DataType

    Parameters: - when additional information are required(for exp: to reverse String we need to pass string)

Branching Statements:
        Break: Jump from loop and switch statements
        Continue: Jump from specific Iterations from the loop
        Return: jump/exit the methods and return the value of the methods